<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧ - <span class="c2">(١٤٧١)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَاهُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2591">أَبُو الرَّبِيعِ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">وَقُتَيْبَةُ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">حَمَّادٌ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبَ </a>بِهَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ نَحْوَهُ،<span class="c5"> غَيْرَ أَنَّهُ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">« فَسَأَلَ عُمَرُ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَأَمَرَهُ »</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>